Differential Expression plots for Alzheimerâ€™s Proteomics experiments

This analysis consists of proteins pulldown from Tg P301s mice and WT controls. There are also tdTtomato control animals which represents all background proteins.

library(EnhancedVolcano)
library(MSstatsTMT)
library(UniProt.ws)
library(MSstats)
library(readr)

setwd("/gstore/scratch/u/lucast3/Alzheimers_Proteomics/")

Tg P301s BioID vs All other control animals

Here we are making the comparison to see which proteins are enriched in AD animals over controls.

# Read in Differential expression data
data <- read_delim("Tg_BioIDvsAll.csv",
                   delim = ";", escape_double = FALSE,
                   col_types = cols(log2FC = col_number()),
                   locale = locale(decimal_mark = ",", grouping_mark = "."),
                   trim_ws = TRUE)
